dmitry.name: Dmitri
dmitry.biography: Dmitriy is an experienced tattoo artist. He has been involved in tattooing for about 28 years. He works in realistic style. Also, I do tattoo covers.

ketto.name: Ketto
ketto.biography: Kateryna is very close to nature in her work, so birds and flower compositions are patterns she feels great in. The range of skills is very wide: from realism to vipshading style. She feels best in colorful works.
